      "patchset_number": 1,
      "line": 155,
      "message": "there is no need to invoke the whole method again, the distributionClient.init() is all that needs to be invoked.\n\nAs this is all happening in a single thread, any delay in bringing up a reception handler would prevent other reception handlers from coming up. \nWe should spawn a separate thread for performing the init and return from the initializeReception, allowing other reception handlers(should any exist) to be initialized and causing DistributionActivator.alive to be set to true",
